Point Given]]\n|[[Bob Baffert]]\n|[[The Thoroughbred Corp.]]\n|-\n|2000\n|[[Tiznow]]\n|[[Jay M. Robbins]]\n|Michael Cooper & Cecilia Straub-Rubens\n|-\n|1999\n|[[Charismatic (horse)|Charismatic]]\n|[[D. Wayne Lukas]]\n|[[Robert B. Lewis|Bob & Beverly Lewis]]\n|-\n|1998\n|[[Real Quiet]]\n|[[Bob Baffert]]\n|[[Michael E. Pegram]]\n|-\n|1997\n|[[Silver Charm]]\n|[[Bob Baffert]]\n|[[Robert B. Lewis|Bob & Beverly Lewis]]\n|-\n|1996\n|[[Skip Away]]\n|[[Sonny Hine]]\n|[[Sonny Hine|Carolyn Hine]]\n|-\n|1995\n|[[Thunder Gulch]]\n|[[D. Wayne Lukas]]\n|[[Michael Tabor]]\n|-\n|1994\n|[[Holy Bull]]\n|[[Warren A. Croll Jr.]]\n|[[Warren A. Croll Jr.]]\n|-\n|1993\n|[[Prairie Bayou]]\n|[[Thomas Bohannan]]\n|[[Loblolly Stable]]\n|-\n|1992\n|[[A.P. Indy]]\n|[[Neil D. Drysdale]]\n|[[Tomonori Tsurumaki]]\n|-\n|1991\n|[[Hansel (horse)|Hansel]]\n|[[Frank L. Brothers]]\n|[[Joe Allbritton|Lazy Lane Farm]]\n|-\n|1990\n|[[Unbridled]]\n|[[Carl Nafzger]]\n|[[Frances A. Genter]]\n|-\n|1989\n|[[Sunday Silence]]\n|[[Charles E. Whittingham]]\n|[[H-G-W Partners]]\n|-\n|1988\n|[[Risen Star]]\n|[[Louie Roussel III]]\n|Ronnie Lamarque & Louie Roussel III\n|-\n|1987\n|[[Alysheba]]\n|[[Jack Van Berg]]\n|Dorothy & Pamela Scharbauer\n|-\n|1986\n|[[Snow Chief]]\n|[[Melvin F. Stute]]\n|Carl Grinstead & Ben Rochelle\n|-\n|1985\n|[[Spend A Buck]]\n|[[Cam Gambolati]]\n|Hunter Farm\n|-\n|1984\n|[[Swale (horse)|Swale]]\n|[[Woody Stephens]]\n|[[Claiborne Farm]]\n|-\n|1983\n|[[Slew o' Gold]]\n|[[Sidney Watters Jr.]]\n|[[Equusequity Stable]]\n|-\n|1982\n|[[Conquistador Cielo]]\n|[[Woody Stephens]]\n|[[Henryk de Kwiatkowski]]\n|-\n|1981\n|[[Pleasant Colony]]\n|[[John P. Campo]]\n|[[Buckland Farm]]\n|-\n|1980\n|[[Temperence Hill]]\n|[[Joseph B. Cantey]]\n|[[Loblolly Stable]]\n|-\n|1979\n|[[Spectacular Bid]]\n|[[Bud Delp]]\n|Hawksworth Farm\n|-\n|1978\n|[[Affirmed]]\n|[[Laz Barrera]]\n|[[Louis Wolfson|Harbor View Farm]]\n|-\n|1977\n|[[Seattle Slew]]\n|[[William H. Turner Jr.]]\n|Karen & Mickey Taylor\n|-\n|1976\n|[[Bold Forbes]]\n|[[Laz Barrera]]\n|[[Est\u00e9ban Rodriguez Tizol]]\n|-\n|1975\n|[[Wajima (horse)|Wajima]]\n|[[Stephen A. DiMauro]]\n|East-West Stable\n|-\n|1974\n|[[Little Current (horse)|Little Current]]\n|[[Lou Rondinello]]\n|[[Darby Dan Farm]]\n|-\n|1973\n|[[Secretariat (horse)|Secretariat]]\n|[[Lucien Laurin]]\n|[[Penny Chenery|Meadow Stable]]\n|-\n|1972\n|[[Key to the Mint]]\n|[[J. Elliott Burch]]\n|[[Rokeby Stables]]\n|-\n|1971\n|[[Canonero II]]\n|[[Juan Arias (horse trainer)|Juan Arias]]\n|Pedro Baptista\n|}\n\n===Daily Racing Form, Turf & Sport Digest and Thoroughbred Racing Association Awards===\n{| class = \"wikitable sortable\" | border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; font-size:90%\"\n|-  style=\"background:#987654; text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width:42px;\"| '''Year'''<br>\n! style=\"width:175px;\"| '''Horse'''<br>\n! style=\"width:165px;\"| '''Trainer'''<br>\n! style=\"width:250px;\"| '''Owner'''<br>\n|-\n|1970\n|[[Personality (horse)|Personality]]\n|[[John W. Jacobs]]\n|[[Ethel D. Jacobs]]\n|-\n|1969\n|[[Arts and Letters]]\n|[[J. Elliott Burch]]\n|[[Rokeby Stables]]\n|-\n|1968\n|[[Stage Door Johnny]] (TRA)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=gJBYAAAAIBAJ&sjid=QfgDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7061,785404&dq=stage-door-johnny&hl=en |title=Dark Mirage wins honor |publisher=Spokane Daily Chronicle |date=December 4, 1968 |accessdate=2012-07-13}}</ref> (DRF)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=bGNLAAAAIBAJ&sjid=wCMNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1622,6319262&dq=stage-door-johnny&hl=en |title=Unprecedented turf sweep by Dr Fager |publisher=Press-Courier |date=November 28, 1968 |accessdate=2012-07-13}}</ref>\n|[[John M. Gaver, Sr.]]\n|[[Greentree Stable]]\n|-\n|1968\n|[[Forward Pass (horse)|Forward Pass]] (TSD)<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=6XkyAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GrkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3746,3287451&dq=forward-pass&hl=en |title=Dr Fager Named top horse |publisher=Montreal Gazette |date=November 13, 1968 |accessd