AJ |oclc=31870180 |ref=harv }}\n* {{cite book |author=Satish Chandra |author-link=Satish Chandra |title=History of Medieval India: 800-1700 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qHnHHwAACAAJ |year=2007 |publisher=Orient Longman |isbn=978-81-250-3226-7 |ref=harv }}\n{{ref end}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{commons category}}\n{{wikiquote}}\n\n{{Turkic topics|state=collapsed}}\n{{Authority control}}\n[[Category:Historical Turkic states]]\n[[Category:States and territories established in 1206]]\n[[Category:Delhi Sultanate| ]]\n[[Category:Empires and kingdoms of India]]\n[[Category:Former sultanates]]\n[[Category:Islamic rule in the Indian subcontinent]]\n[[Category:1206 establishments in Asia]]\n[[Category:13th-century establishments in India]]\n[[Category:1526 disestablishments in India]]\n[[Category:States and territories disestablished in 1526]]\n", "name_user": "AdiAbhishek Pathak", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delhi_Sultanate"}
